1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Počinje podcast Mrežnica. Želim vam dobrodošlicu. Naš današnji gost, profesor Petar Popović,

2
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:24,000
